author: Source: Lancashire Telegraph
title: Erik Lamela nets as Tottenham are held to draw by Monaco - Lancashire Telegraph
text:
Erik Lamela's resurgence continued in Monaco but a late Stephan El Shaarawy header denied Tottenham victory in the Europa League. It may have taken two seasons to find any consistency, but the A 30million club-record acquisition from Roma is at last fulfilling his promise.
 Lancashire Telegraph.
